<body>
 <p>
  <b>Rule-8 ᐅ </b>
  Complex এবং compound sentence-যুক্ত Active voice-কে passive-এ পরিণত করার সময় উভয় clause-এর voice পরিবর্তন করা হয়।
 </p>
 <h3>Example ᐅ </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>I know that he sang the song. (Active)</li>
  <li>It is known to me that the song was sung by him. (Passive)</li>
 </ul>
 <p>
  <b>Note ᐅ</b>
  Active voice যদি “People say” দিয়ে শুরু হয়, তবে একে passive করতে হলে, এর শুরুতে “It is said that” ব্যবহৃত হয়।
 </p>
 <h3>Example ᐅ </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>People say that Dhaka is the city of mosques. (Active)</li>
  <li>It is said that Dhaka is the city of mosques. (Passive)</li>
 </ul>
